Install Virtual Box: https://www.virtualbox.org/
Install Windows: https://www.microsoft.com/software-download/windows11
Install Linux: https://www.kali.org/get-kali/

Open Virtual Box:
1. Create new virtual machine for Windows.
2. Create new virtual machine for Linux.
3. In windows vm: 
                 - Install DVWA git -> clone https://github.com/digininja/DVWA.git
                 - Install Xampp -> https://www.apachefriends.org/
                 - Copy DVWA folder and paste in Xampp-> htdocs
                 - Open XAMPP, start Apache and SQL.
                 - Search localhost/dvwa in your browser, if DVWA is successfully hosted on you machine you will DVWA login page in your browser.

